The paper deals with programming language semantics and constructs for decision making on connected spaces such as $\mathbb{R}$, which involves formal logics and pattern matching. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL), and Mathematical Software (cs.MS) sub-categories.
